        "```\n",
        "\n",
        "**Fonctionnement**:\n",
        "\n",
        "1. **Somme pondérée**: $z = w_1x_1 + w_2x_2 + ... + w_nx_n + b$\n",
        "2. **Activation**: $y = f(z)$\n",
        "\n",
        "Où:\n",
        "\n",
        "- $x_i$ = entrées (features)\n",
        "- $w_i$ = poids (weights)\n",
        "- $b$ = biais (bias)\n",
        "- $f$ = fonction d'activation\n",
        "- $y$ = sortie"
