        "\n",
        "**L2 (Ridge)**:\n",
        "$$L_{total} = L_{original} + \\lambda \\sum w^2$$\n",
        "\n",
        "**L1 (Lasso)**:\n",
        "$$L_{total} = L_{original} + \\lambda \\sum |w|$$\n",
        "\n",
        "**Effet**:\n",
        "\n",
        "- Pénalise les poids élevés\n",
        "- Force le modèle à rester simple\n",
